Being a potato would be quite the simple existence! You'd spend your early days growing underground, surrounded by soil, without a care in the world. No deadlines, no social media, just quietly developing your starchy goodness.

Later, you might be harvested and face an uncertain future - perhaps becoming french fries, mashed potatoes, or the star of a potato salad. You'd never travel under your own power, but might see the world from kitchen counters and dinner plates.

